{"tid":2117937,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"健身及舞蹈業界批政府防疫不力 要求合理賠償","createTime":"2020-07-21T07:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T07:16:28.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"46883e3530926d8ff856d935a8f9b32f3b825563","tid":2117937,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"健身及舞蹈業界批政府防疫不力 要求合理賠償<br />\n2020-07-21 HKT 13:17<br />\n<br />\n&quot;受新型肺炎疫情影響，本港多類處所暫停營業，包括美容院、健身中心及按摩院等。健身及舞蹈業界批評，政府防疫把關不力，對業界援助不足，促請盡快落實第三輪防疫抗疫基金，並對業界作出合理賠償。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;健身拳館負責人柯尊鼎表示...已知至少60、70間健身中心結業...疫情至今僅一、兩宗確診發生在大型連鎖健身中心，其他中小型中心根本沒有問題，行內亦做足防疫措施，但政府無視他們的努力。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1539010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1539010&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP7TyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=b1598abf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1539010&h=a85efa35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1539010</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>強制關閉gym，令政府、健身愛好者及健身業界三輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"}]}